                             DEFENDER 2 CONTROLS

Typed in by ZARCH.  Edited by PARASITE.


Move Mouse Up/Down   :   Moves Your Ship Vertically
Left Mouse Button    :   Thrust Ship
Right Mouse Button   :   Reverse Ship
Left Shift Key       :   Fire Weapons
Ctrl Key             :   Release Smart Bomb
Left Alt Key         :   Inviso Mode In Defender Or
                         Smart Laser In Defender II And Stargate
Space Bar            :   Cycle Through Weapons (Defender II Only!)
X Key                :   Quit

More Help Can Be Found In The Games In Built Trainer Mode!

Also Go Into The Options Menu For More Goodies!

end.
